{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_02_02",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 2話 新ユニットのオファー",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――こころに麻奈の昔話を始めて30分後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—30 minutes after starting to talk about Mana’s past",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "――そして、こころ達が加入する前のLizNoirと\n麻奈が対決することが決定した。もう何年も前の話だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And so‚ before you joined LizNoir‚ they were set\nfor a showdown against Mana. This was years ago now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 13.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "テレビで観てました～。中断する前の\nNEXT VENUSグランプリの決勝ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I saw it on TV. The NEXT VENUS Grand Prix‚\nbefore the event was suspended.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。その前日、麻奈と莉央さんは激しくやり合った\n特に麻奈はわざとケンカを売っているように見えた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. The day before‚ Mana and Rio-san really got into it.\nMana in particular really looked like she was picking a fight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 28.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ……\n現場ではそんな険悪な雰囲気だったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?\nI had no idea things were so bad behind the scenes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 33.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんも対抗心むき出しで\n……俺はいつ止めに入ろうかとはらはらしていたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san was spoiling for a fight too.\nI almost had to leap in between them. It was that bad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "だから、帰り道、麻奈に強めに注意したんだ\n麻奈は全然反省してなかったみたいだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So on the way home‚ I had to caution Mana strongly.\nShe didn’t seem especially repentant.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 48.166666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～。思ってたよりも勝ち気な方だったんですね\nステージではいつも笑顔だから、ギャップあります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow. She’s pretty hardcore‚ huh?\nOn stage‚ she’s always so smiley. It’s hard to picture it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "当時は俺も、麻奈の負けん気が災いしたと思った\nでも、今は考え方が変わったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At the time‚ I thought her stubbornness was a problem.\nBut I’ve changed my mind on that now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "……どう変わったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have? How?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 66.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈は100％の莉央さん――リズノワと競いたかった\nだから、わざとそんな態度をとったんだと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana wanted to battle Rio-san—to battle LizNoir at 100%.\nThat’s why she acted up like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈はとにかくファンを大切にしていた……だから\n決勝を最高のステージにしたかったんじゃないかって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana always values her fans‚ above all else.\nShe wanted to give them the best possible performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 83.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……つまり、盛り上げるために\n莉央さんの闘志にわざと火をつけたってことですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… So you’re saying\nshe kicked off a fight with Rio-san for the sake of the live?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことしたら、不利になるだけじゃないですか\n意味分かりませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But surely that would put her at a disadvantage?\nI can’t understand why she’d do that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 95.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そういうやつだったんだよ\n……それに、絶対に勝つ自信があったんだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s just who she was.\nAnd she was probably confident she could win anyway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……今となっては全て、俺の想像だけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All just speculation on my part now‚ of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 106.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、麻奈さんって、可愛くて清楚なお嬢さん\n……って感じのイメージだったんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm. Mana-san seemed like a cute and prim little lady.\nThat was my image of her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに激しい一面があったんですね\nすっごい自信家みたいですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But she’s got a more aggressive side too‚ huh?\nAnd so confident!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 119.83333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "それに見合うだけの努力はしていたよ\n才能だけで伝説のアイドルになった訳じゃないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She worked hard‚ don’t get me wrong.\nShe didn’t become a legend on talent alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 126.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "私だって努力してます！\n才能は……あるかどうか分かりませんけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I work hard too!\nI can’t comment on the talent part‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 133.23333333333332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、笑顔はアイドルの世界で一番です！\n麻奈さんにだって負けませんよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but I’m the idol with the most brilliant smile in the world!\nEven Mana-san can’t match that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 139.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "はは……一番かどうかは分からないけど\n自信を持つのはいいことだと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha. I can’t comment on that either‚\nbut it’s definitely good to be confident.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "どうして目を逸らしながら言うんですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you looking away as you say that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 150.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "でも感謝です。参考になりました\n麻奈さんのいいところを頑張って真似してみます～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I am grateful. You’ve given me a lot to think about.\nI’ll make sure to copy all the best things from Mana-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ほどほどにな……そういえば仕事の話があったんだ\n麻奈の話をしていて忘れるところだったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t overdo it. Hey‚ I have a job for you too.\nI was about to forget‚ after all this Mana talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 166.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "どんなお仕事です？\n私達LizNoirはお安くありませんよ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What kind of work?\nLizNoir doesn’t come cheap!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "今回は、LizNoirじゃない\n星見プロの年少組へのオファーだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This isn’t for LizNoir.\nIt’s an offer to join a young idol group at Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
