    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "こころには、他のグループの年少メンバーと組んで\nテレビで歌ってもらいたいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They want you to form a team with other younger members\nand sing on TV.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "面白そうですね～\n年少メンバーって、他に誰がいるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That does sound like fun!\nWho are the others?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルからは奥山さん、月ストからはすず\n……サニピからは千紗だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okuyama-san from TRINITYAiLE‚ Suzu from Moon Tempest…\nand Chisa from Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど～。中学生のフレッシュな若手だけを\n集めたって訳ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. The fresh-faced middle schoolers.\nThat’s the plan‚ is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "……高校生だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…There’s a high schooler in there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "ん～？　誰がですか？\nみんな中学生じゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? There is?\nThey all look like middle schoolers to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "……千紗は、高校二年生だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Chisa is a second-year at high school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですね～。千紗ちゃんは可愛らしいから\nてっきりこころと同い年くらいだと――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I see~ Chisa is so adorable‚\nI was sure she was my age.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "それは本人には絶対に言うなよ……とにかく\nこの番組だけの一回限りのユニットだけど、どうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Make sure you don’t say that to her. Anyway‚\nthis is a one-off team‚ just for this event. What do you say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんやりますよ！\nこころに目をつけるなんて、センスがありますね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I’ll do it!\nThey’ve got a good eye‚ picking me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "最年長は千紗だけど、ちょっと緊張してるみたいだ\nどうか仲良くな……絶対陰でイジメたりするなよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa is the oldest‚ but I think she’s a little nervous.\nTry and get along… and no picking on her!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr020.m4a",
      "text": "もう、そんなことする訳ないじゃないですか～\n人を腹黒キャラみたいに～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ look who you’re talking to! I would never.\nLike I’m some kind of sinister schemer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 247.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "変なこと言って、いつも愛のせいにしてるのは\n誰だよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who’s the one always saying weird stuff\nand pinning it on Ai?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr021.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃんはこころにかまわれるのが好きなんです\nこころの愛情表現の一バリエーションにすぎませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai-chan loves it when I mess with her.\nIt’s just one way Kokoro express the affection.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr022.m4a",
      "text": "こころは、誰にでも優しい\nみんなのアイドルなんですから～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro is kind to everyone‚\nand everyone’s idol!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.53333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_02-kkr023.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ～ん、麻奈さんみたいな凄いステージに\nしてみせますから、期待してて下さいね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe! I’ll make it a fantastic performance\nworthy of Mana-san! Look forward to it!",
        "id": ""
